    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways. Everything runs smoothly, and it's been well-loved and looked after! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is definitely the one for you. Can't wait for it to find a great new home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
